               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikaʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St. Michael (fols. 5ra-60ra) &#xD;
I-1) Introduction (fols. 5ra-7ra) &#xD;
I-2) Homily by Timothy (Dämatewos), [Patriarch] of Alexandria [for Ḫǝdar] (fols. 7ra-12ra); miracle (fol. 12ra-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 12vb-13ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 13ra-rb) &#xD;
I-3) Homily by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs the Orthodox for the 12th of Taḫśaś [Miyazya] (fols. 13rb-16rb); miracle (fols. 16rb-17ra); commemorative notice (fol. 17ra-rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 17rb-va) &#xD;
I-4) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th of Ṭǝrr [Taḫśaś] (fols. 17va-21va); miracle (fol. 21va-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 21vb-22ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 22ra-rb) &#xD;
I-5) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th of Yäkkatit (fols. 22rb-24rb); miracle (fol. 24rb-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 24vb-25ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 25ra-rb) &#xD;
I-6) Homily by Yoḥannǝs [Severus], Metropolitan [Patriarch] of Antiochia for the 12th of Mäggabit (fols. 25rb-34va); miracle (fols. 34va-35rb); commemorative notice (fol. 35rb) &#xD;
I-7) Homily [by Epiphanius, Metropolitan of Cyprus] for the 12th of Miyazya [Ṭǝrr] (fols. 35va-39rb); miracle (fols. 39rb-40rb); commemorative notice (fol. 40rb-va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 40va) &#xD;
I-8) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Ethiopia for Gǝnbot (fols. 40va-41vb); miracle (fols. 41vb-42va); commemorative notice (fol. 42va-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fols. 42vb-43ra) &#xD;
I-9) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of ʾAksum (ʾAkwǝsǝm) for Säne (fols. 43ra-46vb); miracle (fols. 46vb-47vb); commemorative notice (fols. 47vb-48rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 48rb) &#xD;
I-10) Homily by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs for Ḥamle (fols. 48rb-51rb); miracle (fol. 51rb-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 51vb-52ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 52ra-rb) &#xD;
I-11) Homily by an anonymous author for Näḥase (fols. 52rb-54rb); miracle (fol. 54rb-vb); commemorative notice (fol. 54vb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 55ra) &#xD;
I-12) Homily by an anonymous author for Mäskäräm (fols. 55ra-56va); miracle (fol. 56va-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 56vb-57ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 57ra) &#xD;
I-13) Homily by an anonymous author for Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 57ra-59rb); miracle (fol. 59rb-va); commemorative notice (fols. 59va-60ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 60ra) &#xD;
II) Malkǝʾa Mikaʾel "Image of Michael" (fols. 60rb-63ra) &#xD;
III) Unidentified text (fol. 63rb-vb).</summary>
